  "detailed_description": "Magnet Block is a simple 3d sokoban puzzle game.<br><br>The goal is to exit each puzzle through the teleporter.<br>Doing so requires the use and exploitation of the titular magnetically monopole blocks.<br><br>Opposites attract - Identical repulse.<br>The rules are simple but there are non trivial consequences to the world state.<br><br>Take the journey through 107 puzzles. No filler.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092660/extras/92c5e093ddab463e3490e5572b09a6f9.poster.avif?t=1732607480\" width=522 height=578 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092660/extras/92c5e093ddab463e3490e5572b09a6f9.webm?t=1732607480\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2092660/extras/92c5e093ddab463e3490e5572b09a6f9.mp4?t=1732607480\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
